# USAGE: the intent of this file is to keep track of current
# regressions and to keep notes about why they are failing.  Since
# linux is our main platform, linux regressions are listed first, and
# are typically assumed to apply to all other platforms as well.
# Other platforms/settings that are currently causing regressions are
# listed afterwards in no particular order.  Formatting for each entry
# can be loose, but should roughly follow the format of brief note on
# why the test is failing followed by a list of tests that are failing
# for that reason.  If someone owns a particular regression, their
# name can be added to the description as well.

